<h1>Welcome to Rock Paper Scissors!</h1>

<%= image_tag("games/rock-paper-scissors.jpg", :alt => "rock paper scissors") %>

<p>To play this game, all you have to do is pick rock, paper, or scissors. If your pick matches the computer's, you win!</p>

<p>Choose carefully... you only get one try!</p>

<br/>

<h2>Pick rock, paper, or scissors:<h2>

<% @rock_paper_scissors.each do |number| %>
  <%= link_to image_tag("rock_paper_scissors/#{number}.jpg"), rock_paper_scissor_path(number) %>
<% end %>
